    "description": "If you're a passionate Financial Analyst with drive and ambition, Sharekhan Global Group in Patna is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Sharekhan Global Group:\nSharekhan Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in GST\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sharekhan Global Group!",
